This is the email template for users to pay for their deductible coverage.

We can put cool things like the following:

Vehicle Information:

        VIN:  <%= @vehicle.vin %>
     Make:   <%= @vehicle.make %>
    Model:   <%= @vehicle.model %>

To initiate your coverage for the above vehicle use the link below to securely pay for your subscribtion.

<%= pay_url(@vehicle.policy_id, @vehicle.id, :host=>'localhost:3000') %>
